UID:bam-scanteia-bucharest-residency-2026-2027@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260529T085824Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260607
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260608
SUMMARY:Deadline: Bayt AlMamzar x Scanteia: Bucharest Residency Exchange 20
 26-2027
DESCRIPTION:An international exchange between Bayt AlMamzar (BAM)\, an arti
 st-run space in Dubai\, and Scanteia\, an artist-run space in Bucharest\, 
 inviting UAE-based artists to undertake individual month-long residencies 
 in Bucharest across 2026-2027\, followed by a joint exhibition curated by 
 Scanteia. Two artists are selected for non-overlapping residencies (Aug-Se
 p 2026 and mid-March to mid-April 2027). Scanteia provides a private ~50 s
 qm studio with live-in accommodation\, a flight subsidy up to $500\, a $50
 0 artist fee\, a local transport card\, weekly studio visits with Romanian
  curators and gallerists\, study trips (MARe\, MNAC\, EVA Foundation)\, ac
 cess to specialised equipment (large-scale inkjet printing\, photography s
 tudio\, wood workshop\, scanners)\, exhibition space\, and documentation/p
 ublication support via BAM's publishing arm BAMBAM. ELIGIBILITY: open to v
 isual artists\, researchers and practitioners currently based in the UAE\,
  aged 18+\, at any career stage\; a valid UAE residence visa is required a
 t the time of application. No nationality restriction\, but applicants wit
 hout an EU or Emirati passport will need a Schengen visa (Scanteia provide
 s an invitation letter). They seek artists with a developed practice and a
  specific\, articulable reason to spend time in Bucharest (exploration\, r
 esearch\, production or exchange)\, with no fixed theme or medium. Deadlin
 e 7 June 2026. Contact hello@baytalmazmar.org.\n\nOrganisation: Bayt AlMam
 zar (BAM) and Scanteia\nLocation: Residency in Bucharest\, Romania (applic
 ants must be UAE-based)\nAward: Funded residency: private ~50 sqm studio w
 ith accommodation at Atelierele Scanteia\, flight covered up to $500\, $50
 0 artist fee\, local transport card\, access to large-format inkjet printi
 ng\, photo studio\, wood workshop and scanners\, plus a curated joint exhi
 bition. No application fee.\nDuration: One month (Residency 1: Aug-Sep 202
 6\; Residency 2: mid-March to mid-April 2027)\, with a joint exhibition en
 d of April 2027\n\nMore: https://www.prazzlearts.com/opportunities/open-ca
 ll-for-artist-residency-bam--scnteia-bucharest-2027
URL:https://www.prazzlearts.com/opportunities/open-call-for-artist-residenc
 y-bam--scnteia-bucharest-2027
LOCATION:Residency in Bucharest\, Romania (applicants must be UAE-based)
END:VEVENT
