 y 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Film Independent\nLocation: Los Angeles\, US\nAwa
 rd: Multiple bundled fellowships for selected fellows: Amazon MGM Studios 
 ($10\,000)\, Climate Entertainment Commissioning Grant ($25\,000 for a new
