 finalists. Deadline 1 June 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Reply\nLocation: Online 
 submissions\; premiere event in Venice\, Italy\nAward: First prize EUR 8\,
 000\, second prize EUR 5\,000\, third prize EUR 2\,000 (total prize pool E
 UR 30\,000+)\, plus travel and 2-night Venice accommodation for finalists.
