 ed media\; current students are not eligible. Submit via SlideRoom. Applic
 ations for the 2027 cycle are open through 1 July 2026.\n\nOrganisation: L
 ight Work\nLocation: Syracuse\, New York\, United States\nAward: $7\,500 s
 tipend plus furnished housing and 24-hour access to Light Work's digital l
