 hub.io
DTSTAMP:20260529T085824Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260531
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260601
SUMMARY:Deadline: Malakta x Kulturhuset Dux: Community Art Commission and R
 esidency 2026 (Kristinestad)
DESCRIPTION:Commission and residency from Art in Malakta rf with Kulturhuse
 t Dux and Kristinestad Artist Residency to create a public artwork for Kul
 turhuset Dux or its immediate surroundings\, in dialogue with Kristinestad
  and its residents. The medium is open (installation\, object\, sound\, te
 xtile\, light\, digital)\; what matters is the relationship between the wo
 rk\, the site and the people. The project is rooted in Kristinestad's iden
 tity as a Cittaslow town and as Baltic Sea Cultural Pearl 2026. PHASE 1 (1
  Sep - 4 Oct 2026): a one-month residency at Kristinestad Artist Residency
  for research\, meetings\, workshops\, and artistic development. PHASE 2: 
 production after the residency (remotely or at Malakta if needed)\; the ar
 twork must be completed by summer 2027 and requires on-site presence. ELIG
 IBILITY: open to artists or artist collectives wanting to work site-specif
 ically and in dialogue with residents. APPLY by email to communityart@mala
 kta.fi by 31 May 2026 with a motivation letter\, portfolio\, CV and websit
 e link as a single PDF (max 5 MB). Interviews before 19 June 2026.\n\nOrga
 nisation: Art in Malakta rf (with Kulturhuset Dux and Kristinestad Artist 
 Residency)\nLocation: Kristinestad / Malax\, Finland\nAward: EUR 6\,000 ar
 tist fee plus EUR 5\,000 materials budget\, with travel and residency acco
 mmodation included. No application fee.\nDuration: One-month residency 1 S
 ep - 4 Oct 2026 (Phase 1) plus production phase\, with artwork completed b
 y summer 2027 (Phase 2)\n\nMore: https://www.malakta.fi/community-art-in-k
 ristinestad-kulturhuset-dux/
URL:https://www.malakta.fi/community-art-in-kristinestad-kulturhuset-dux/
LOCATION:Kristinestad / Malax\, Finland
END:VEVENT
